sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Geopolitical Analyst
    participant UI as Graph Explorer (React)
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Neo4j as Neo4j Graph DB
    participant Analyzer as Path Analysis Service

    User->>UI: Select Source & Target Entities
    UI->>API: POST /api/v1/graph/paths (source_id, target_id)
    API->>Neo4j: Execute ShortestPath / AllPaths (Cypher)
    Neo4j-->>API: Raw Graph Topology
    
    API->>Analyzer: Analyze Paths & Bridges
    Note over Analyzer: Calculate hop distances &<br/>identify intermediate nodes
    Analyzer-->>API: Structured Path Analysis Report
    
    API-->>UI: JSON (Nodes, Edges, Executive Summary)
    
    UI->>UI: Render Force-Directed Graph
    UI->>User: Interactive Visualization + Path Descriptions
